<x-showcase title="PackagingDirect" subtitle="A multistore B2B Rapidez webshop" image="/img/cases/rozenkelim.png">
    <p>PackagingDirect BV is the e-commerce company behind multiple specialized online shops in disposables and packaging. They provide more than 20.000 customers a year with a complete range of sustainable and innovative products but also offer a wide selection of custom-printed disposables and reusable packaging</p>
    <p>PackagingDirect is a multistore B2B Rapidez webshop and incorporates features such as dynamic product options from an external API, Kiyoh product reviews integration and seamless integration with the JustBetter checkout theme package. Within the checkout Multisafepay, Serverside Analytics and PostNL are integrated to ensure a smooth and efficient checkout process with pickup locations.</p>
    <p>Additionally there are several Statamic integrations, utilizing Runway to make it possible to link entries to Magento products and categories. Statamic also facilitates dynamic form creation, enabling form submissions with PDF generation for quote requests and it offers convenient management of multilanguage and multisite shop content.</p>
</x-showcase>
